Agile Maneuvers										CATEGORY:FEAT		TYPE:Combat																																																																																																											DESC:You learned to use your quickness in place of brute force when performing combat maneuvers.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																														BONUS:VAR|CMB_STAT|DEX-STR|PRESIZEGT:T																																												SOURCEPAGE:p.117																																																																					BENEFIT:You add your Dexterity bonus to your base attack bonus and size bonus when determining your Combat Maneuver Bonus (see Chapter 8) instead of your Strength bonus.
