Craft Wand											CATEGORY:FEAT		TYPE:ItemCreation																																			PREMULT:1,[PRECLASS:1,SPELLCASTER=5],[PREVARGTEQ:CasterLevel_Highest,5]																																																												DESC:You can create magic wands.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																											SOURCEPAGE:p.120																																																																					BENEFIT:You can create a wand of any 4th-level or lower spell that you know. Crafting a wand takes 1 day for each 1,000 gp in its base price. To craft a wand, you must use up raw materials costing half of this base price. A newly created wand has 50 charges. See the magic item creation rules in Chapter 15 for more information.
