Leadership											CATEGORY:FEAT		TYPE:General																																PRELEVEL:MIN=7																																																DEFINE:LeadershipMaxCohortLvl|0	DEFINE:LeadershipScore|0	DEFINE:LeadershipAbilityScoreMod|0								DESC:You attract followers to your cause and a companion to join you on your adventure.																																																																										ABILITY:FEAT|VIRTUAL|Leadership Score																																																																																																																																																																																																																BONUS:VAR|LeadershipMaxCohortLvl|min((TL-2),(((LeadershipScore+6)*7)/10)-4)	BONUS:VAR|LeadershipScore|(TL+LeadershipAbilityScoreMod)	BONUS:VAR|LeadershipAbilityScoreMod|CHA																					SOURCEPAGE:p.129																																																																					BENEFIT:This feat enables you to attract a loyal cohort and a number of devoted subordinates who assist you. A cohort is generally an NPC with class levels, while followers are typically lower level NPCs. See Table 5-2 for what level of cohort and how many followers you can recruit.
Lightning Reflexes									CATEGORY:FEAT		TYPE:General																																																																																																										DESC:You have faster reflexes than normal.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																							BONUS:SAVE|Reflex|2																																																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.130																																																																					BENEFIT:You get a +2 bonus on all Reflex saving throws.
