Spellbreaker										CATEGORY:FEAT		TYPE:Combat						PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Disruptive																																																															PREVARGTEQ:SpellBreakerQualify,1																											DESC:You can strike at enemy spellcasters who fail to cast defensively when you threaten them.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																	SOURCEPAGE:p.134																																																																					BENEFIT:Enemies in your threatened area that fail their checks to cast spells defensively provoke attacks of opportunity from you.
